_sText:
cs_747_css is a port of cs_747 to Source. The autogenerated navmesh is full of errors, so I sought out to fix it.
Several improvements listed below
1. Ladders can now be used
2. Vents can now be used, and the dropdown vent into LongHall is now usable by the bots.
3. Less suicidal jumping.
4. Map is place-named as accurately to the 1.6 map as possible
